Sentencas: Nd2NiO4+delta (NNO)-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-delta (CGO) composites were further investigated as cathodes for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells (IT-SOFCs).
Titulo: Performance of Nd2NiO4+δ-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ Composite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The effects of sintering temperature and the relative proportions of NNO and CGO on the cell performances were systematically investigated.
Titulo: Performance of Nd2NiO4+δ-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ Composite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Planar NiO-YSZ anode -supported cells in commercial size of 50 mmx50 mm were fabricated by tape casting, screen printing and co-sintering methods.
Titulo: Performance of Nd2NiO4+δ-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ Composite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: A single cell consisted of a NiO-YSZ anode support, a NiO-YSZ anode interlayer, a YSZ electrolyte layer, a CGO interlayer, a NNO-CGO composite cathode layer, and a La0.6Sr0.4CoO3-delta (LSC) current collector from anode to cathode.
Titulo: Performance of Nd2NiO4+δ-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ Composite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The results show that the cell with 7ONNO-30CGO composite cathode sintered at 1000 degrees C exhibits the highest power density of 385 mW/cm(2) at 0.7 V at 800 degrees C.
Titulo: Performance of Nd2NiO4+δ-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ Composite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The ohmic resistance, polarization resistance and area specific resistance are 0.31, 0.266 and 0.576 Omega center dot cm(2), respectively.
Titulo: Performance of Nd2NiO4+δ-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ Composite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The analysis of electrochemical impedance spectra indicates that the polarization resistance mainly comes from charge transfer resistance.
Titulo: Performance of Nd2NiO4+δ-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ Composite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: SEM image of the cross-section of the cell after testing reveals that each layer has a good adhesion.
Titulo: Performance of Nd2NiO4+δ-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ Composite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Meanwhile, compared with previous research, it can be concluded that adding a CGO interlayer in the single cells leads to an increase in the ohmic resistances and a decrease in the power densities, whereas the values of the polarization resistances decrease.
Titulo: Performance of Nd2NiO4+δ-Ce0.8Gd0.2O2-δ Composite Cathodes for Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
